description:
Danny recaps this week's Lohan Beach Club and chats with cast member Kailah Casillas. Kailah gives us the rundown of working with Lindsay and Panos, the layout of the resort, and so much more! Danny also recaps this week's #RHONJ finale, which featured a wet Marty and an ambush makeover.


Kailah: 9:40ish

RHONJ Recap: 30:13ish
